name: Midnight Blossom
description: A mysterious woman with long, flowing black hair and piercing red eyes, adorned in a dark kimono with cherry blossom patterns.
flavor_text: Whispers of the night, as deadly as she is beautiful.

name: Scarlet Ember
description: A fiery redhead with glowing eyes, wearing a revealing crimson dress that seems to shimmer like flames.
flavor_text: Passion and danger, her heart burns brighter than any inferno.

name: Lunar Priestess
description: A serene beauty with silver hair and glowing blue eyes, wearing a flowing white robe adorned with moon symbols.
flavor_text: Guardian of the night sky, her grace is as cold as the moon.

name: Blood Rose
description: A sultry woman with dark hair and piercing green eyes, wearing a black leather corset adorned with roses.
flavor_text: Thorns as sharp as her wit, every kiss is a promise of pain.

name: Shattered Mirage
description: A mysterious woman with short, spiky white hair and golden eyes, wearing a sleek black and silver outfit.
flavor_text: Illusions are her weapon, but her beauty is all too real.

name: Crimson Valkyrie
description: A strong and confident woman with long blonde hair and crimson wings, wearing a revealing armor set.
flavor_text: War is her passion, and the battlefield is her home.

name: Phantom Dancer
description: A graceful woman with black and purple hair, wearing a revealing outfit that seems to shift like shadows.
flavor_text: Dance with her, but beware the final step.

name: Gilded Siren
description: A golden-haired beauty with piercing blue eyes, wearing a shimmering gold and white dress.
flavor_text: Her song lures you in, but the cost may be your soul.

name: Ashen Widow
description: A dark-haired woman with pale skin and red eyes, wearing a black widow's veil and dress.
flavor_text: Her touch is as cold as the grave, but her love is eternal.

name: Frostbite Seraphim
description: A chilling beauty with white hair and icy blue eyes, wearing a revealing outfit made of frozen crystals.
flavor_text: Her kiss is as cold as the frost, but her heart burns with fire.

name: Nocturnal Huntress
description: A sleek woman with dark hair and glowing yellow eyes, wearing a black leather outfit adorned with wolf symbols.
flavor_text: The night is her domain, and you are her prey.

name: Burning Halo
description: A fiery woman with orange hair and wings, wearing a revealing outfit that seems to be made of pure flames.
flavor_text: Her passion is as hot as the sun, but her love is a burning inferno.

name: Void Empress
description: A mysterious woman with purple hair and black eyes, wearing a dark, revealing outfit adorned with stars.
flavor_text: Her embrace is as empty as the void, but her power is beyond comprehension.

name: Shattered Doll
description: A broken yet beautiful woman with porcelain skin and red hair, wearing a torn white dress.
flavor_text: Her beauty is fragile, but her spirit is unbreakable.

name: Raven's Call
description: A dark-haired woman with black wings and red eyes, wearing a revealing black outfit.
flavor_text: Her call is as mysterious as the night, but her love is as deep as the abyss.

name: Celestial Blade
description: A heavenly woman with white hair and blue eyes, wearing a revealing armor set adorned with wings.
flavor_text: Her blade shines as bright as the stars, but her heart is as cold as space.

name: Blood Moon Enchantress
description: A sultry woman with black hair and red eyes, wearing a revealing outfit adorned with moon symbols.
flavor_text: Her enchantments are as powerful as the blood moon, but her love is a curse.

name: Golden Temptress
description: A blonde woman with golden eyes, wearing a shimmering gold and white dress.
flavor_text: Her beauty is as tempting as gold, but her heart is worth more than any treasure.

name: Stormbringer
description: A powerful woman with wild blue hair and lightning eyes, wearing a revealing outfit that seems to crackle with electricity.
flavor_text: Her touch is as electrifying as the storm, but her love is as calm as the eye of the hurricane.

name: Ashen Widow
description: A dark-haired woman with pale skin and red eyes, wearing a black widow's veil and dress.
flavor_text: Her touch is as cold as the grave, but her love is eternal.
